Name: Warburg micro syndrome 1
Definition: A Warburg micro syndrome that has_material_basis_in autosomal recessive inheritance of homozygous or compound heterozygous mutation in the RAB3GAP1 gene on chromosome 2q21.

Name: Warburg micro syndrome 2
Definition: A Warburg micro syndrome that has_material_basis_in autosomal recessive inheritance of homozygous or compound heterozygous mutation in the RAB3GAP2 gene on chromosome 1q41.

Name: Warburg micro syndrome 3
Definition: A Warburg micro syndrome that has_material_basis_in autosomal recessive inheritance of homozygous or compound heterozygous mutation in the RAB18 gene on chromosome 10p12.

Name: Warburg micro syndrome 4
Definition: A Warburg micro syndrome that has_material_basis_in autosomal recessive inheritance of homozygous or compound heterozygous mutation in the TBC1D20 gene on chromosome 20p13.
